social_posts.post_text: Changing digits, not habits

Yesterday @andyrementer organized the best surprise, putting together messages from my friends scattered around the globe. You know who you are. Thank you for making my day extra special. I was moved to tears 💝 thank you / grazie / gracias
2022, the year of connecting *in person* with people and places I love 📸 Buenos Aires, LA, Trieste, Beaverton, Venice, Udine

From sketches to final details I helped @andyrementer develop Ocean Friends: a public art installation in Hong Kong. Part of #ddHK Vivid Tsuen Wan, organized by Tourism Commission of Hong Kong, curated and executed by @wod_hk. Congrats to all the artists and parts involved. It’s a honor to be here to see months of work coming to life 💙 #designdistricthongkong
